  | newspaper = Ennahar Online English
  | location = Hydra <U+2013> Alger
  | publisher = El Athir For the Press
  | date = 13 December 2009
  | url = http://www.ennaharonline.com/en/international/2612.html
  | accessdate = 16 December 2009}}
</ref> [[Swastika]] in black paint, "[[Sieg Heil]]" in German, "[[Mitterrand and the far right|France to the French]]" in French, and "[[White nationalism#White power|White Power]]" in English were scrawled on the [[mosque]].<ref>
